      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个完整的认证流程图，展示Web客户端、Keycloak和Synapse服务器之间的交互。Web客户端是公有的，Synapse服务器是机密客户端，都要向Keycloak注册。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server",
