        "Keycloak",
        "Synapse Server"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Synapse注册时需要提供client_id和client_secret，属于机密客户端凭证流；Web客户端只用client_id，是公开的，后面走授权码流程加PKCE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Synapse Server",
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "client_credentials",
        "client_id",
        "client_secret"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上初始设置阶段，标注两个注册步骤。接下来是认证流程，Web客户端向Keycloak发起授权码请求对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initial Setup",
        "Web Client (Public)",
        "Keycloak",
