    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，然后Keycloak重定向返回授权码，Web客户端再用code加client_id去换token，拿到access token和refresh token。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Redirect with Auth Code",
